passages.text: The MXAPJ Index dropped \(0.3\%\) to Australia and Korea markets outperformed, while Taiwan and Philippines markets underperformed. Within MXAPJ sectors, Financials and Industrials led while Cons Disc and Info Tech lagged. MSCI Japan rose \(1.1\%\) today.
For a detailed analysis, please see Asian Equity Perspectives: Favorable trajectory but risk of an air pocket, Aug 1, 2025.

Exhibit 1: The MXAPJ index has gained \(16.7\%\) YTD after gaining \(8\%\) in 2024, particularly led by Korea and Hong Kong markets while dragged down by Indonesia, Thailand, and India. Sectorally, Comm Serv and Industrials are leaders in 2025.
